cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.RO 

The paper deals with object classification using 3D data and proposes improvements to both volumetric CNNs and multi-view CNNs. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. The paper also involves analysis of existing approaches and design choices, which could be relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) research. The use of 3D data could also be relevant to graphics (cs.GR) and robotics (cs.RO) research.
